---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Insights"
  description="Practical insights on technical debt, content strategy, analytics integrity, and what we've learned from auditing sites."
>
  <Section class="pt-28 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="mb-6">Insights</h1>
      <p class="text-secondary-text text-xl leading-relaxed">
        What we learn from auditing sites, turned into practical knowledge.
        Technical debt, content strategy, analytics integrity, and the patterns
        we see across every engagement.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section elevated>
    <div class="text-center py-12">
      <p class="text-secondary-text text-lg mb-4">
        Articles are coming in Phase 2.
      </p>
      <p class="text-secondary-text">
        First up: technical debt &amp; revenue, content gaps, analytics integrity,
        and why most audits are useless.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
